22
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:36,400
sensitive when there are differences between
partners in what is a taboo and what people

23
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:43,400
do not want to know. We also need to be very
careful to... not to destroy trust in a collaboration

24
00:02:43,799 --> 00:02:50,799
