35
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:51,690
The important realisation for me when I first
learnt about Mike's work over a decade ago

36
00:03:51,690 --> 00:03:55,479
was that when we want to make change happen,
it is not just important to bring what we

37
00:03:55,479 --> 00:04:01,840
know to bear, but also what we don't know.
During this series of lectures we covered

38
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:06,590
tactics used to stop change from happening
when those with vested interests -- especially

39
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:13,590
money and power -- are threatened. These tactics
include manufacturing ignorance, withholding

40
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:20,590
information, proliferating disinformation,
inhibiting curiosity, and in extreme cases

41
00:04:21,109 --> 00:04:27,000
censorship and oppression.
Finally, a theme that I introduced is the

42
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:32,270
